<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Jesuh Khrih zaangfahnak kha, Lawm in sa cio tuah u; Vawlei vialte
 a zelh lai ca, Nan lunglawm cio tuah u!

[C1]
   A kan khamhnak thawngtha kha, Atu a tlung cang, A kan Khambawi Jesuh
   nih, Atu an khamh cang.

[V2]
 Mitcaw mi nih Jesuh zoh u, Ngaihchiami lawm tuah u; Jesuh nih an
 chuahter cang hna, Thong chung ummi lawm tuah.

[C2]
   A kan khamhnak thawngtha kha, Atu a tlung cang, A kan Khambawi Jesuh
   nih, Atu an khamh cang.

[V3]
 A kan dawt ca Jesuh a thi, thangthat a tlak ngaingai; Vawlei cungah
 daihnak um seh, Pathian thangtha ko seh.

[C3]
   A kan khamhnak thawngtha kha, Atu a tlung cang, A kan Khambawi Jesuh
   nih, Atu an khamh cang.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>KHAMHNAK CH105</title>
<hymn_number>105</hymn_number>
</song>